        <p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of South Carolina, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
